\c 10
\s Impondo zesiliva
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 2 Zenzele impondo ezimbili zesiliva, uzenze zibe ngumsebenzi okhandiweyo\x + Eks. 25.18.\x*; njalo zizakuba ngezakho ekubizeni inhlangano lekusukeni kwezinkamba\x + Isa. 1.13.\x*.
\v 3 Uba bezivuthela inhlangano yonke izabuthana kuwe emnyango wethente lenhlangano\x + Jer. 4.5. Jow. 2.15.\x*.
\v 4 Kodwa uba bevuthela olulodwa, iziphathamandla, inhloko zezinkulungwane zakoIsrayeli zizabuthana kuwe\x + 1.16; 7.2. Eks. 18.21.\x*.
\v 5 Lapho lihlaba umkhosi\x + 31.6.\x*, izinkamba ezimise ngempumalanga zizasuka\x + 2.3; 10.14.\x*.
\v 6 Lalapho lihlaba umkhosi ngokwesibili, izinkamba ezimise ngeningizimu zizasuka\x + 2.10; 10.18.\x*. Bazahlaba umkhosi\x + 31.6.\x* ukuze zisuke.
\v 7 Kodwa ekubuthaniseni ibandla lizavuthela \add impondo\add*, kodwa lingahlabi umkhosi\x + 10.9. Jow. 2.1.\x*.
\v 8 Njalo amadodana kaAroni, abapristi, azavuthela izimpondo\x + 1 Lan. 15.24; 2 Lan. 13.12. Josh. 6.4.\x*. Zizakuba kini yisimiso esilaphakade ezizukulwaneni zenu.
\v 9 Njalo lapho liphuma impi elizweni lakini ukuyakulwa lesitha\x + 31.6; 2 Lan. 13.14. Josh. 6.5.\x* esilicindezelayo\x + Hlu. 2.18; 4.3.\x*, lihlabe umkhosi ngezimpondo, njalo likhunjulwe phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu, lisindiswe ezitheni zenu\x + Gen. 8.1.\x*.
\v 10 Langosuku lwentokozo yenu, lemikhosini yenu emisiweyo\x + 2 Lan. 5.12; 7.6; 29.26. Ezra 3.10. Neh. 12.35. Nani 29.1. Levi 23.24.\x*, lekuthwaseni kwenyanga zenu, lizavuthela izimpondo phezu kweminikelo yenu yokutshiswa laphezu kwemihlatshelo yeminikelo yenu yokuthula\x + Hlab. 81.3. Nani 28.11.\x*, ukuze ibe kini yisikhumbuzo phambi kukaNkulunkulu wenu. NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu.
\s Ukusuka kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli eSinayi
\p
\v 11 Kwasekusithi ngomnyaka wesibili, ngenyanga yesibili, ngolwamatshumi amabili lwenyanga, iyezi laphakanyiswa lisuka phezu kwethabhanekele lobufakazi\x + 9.17.\x*.
\v 12 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebesuka enkangala yeSinayi\x + Eks. 19.1,2. Nani 1.1; 9.5.\x* ngokwenhambo zabo\x + Eks. 40.36.\x*; leyezi lema enkangala yeParani\x + Gen. 14.6; 21.21. Nani 12.16; 13.3,26. Dute. 1.1.\x*.
\v 13 Basebesuka okokuqala ngokomlayo weN\nd kosi\nd* ngesandla sikaMozisi\x + 10.5,6; 2.9,16,24,31,34.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Kwasekusuka uphawu lwenkamba yabantwana bakoJuda kuqala ngamabutho abo\x + 2.3-9.\x*; laphezu kwebutho lakhe kwakunguNashoni indodana kaAminadaba\x + 1.7-9.\x*.
\v 15 Laphezu kwebutho lesizwe sabantwana bakoIsakari kwakunguNethaneli indodana kaZuwari.
\v 16 Laphezu kwebutho lesizwe sabantwana bakoZebuluni kwakunguEliyabi indodana kaHeloni.
\v 17 Ithabhanekele laselidilizwa; amadodana kaGerishoni lamadodana kaMerari asesuka\x + 1.51.\x*, ethwele ithabhanekele\x + 4.24,31; 7.6-8.\x*.
\p
\v 18 Kwasekusuka uphawu lwenkamba yakoRubeni ngamabutho abo\x + 2.10-16.\x*; laphezu kwebutho lakhe kwakunguElizuri indodana kaShedewuri\x + 1.5,6,14.\x*.
\v 19 Laphezu kwebutho lesizwe sabantwana bakoSimeyoni kwakunguShelumiyeli indodana kaZurishadayi.
\v 20 Laphezu kwebutho lesizwe sabantwana bakoGadi kwakunguEliyasafi indodana kaDehuweli.
\v 21 Kwasekusuka amaKohathi ethwele indlu engcwele, l\add abanye\add* bamisa ithabhanekele, engakafiki\x + 4.4,15; 7.9.\x*.
\p
\v 22 Kwasekusuka uphawu lwenkamba yabantwana bakoEfrayimi ngamabutho abo\x + 2.18-24.\x*; laphezu kwebutho lakhe kwakunguElishama indodana kaAmihudi\x + 1.10,11.\x*.
\v 23 Laphezu kwebutho lesizwe sabantwana bakoManase kwakunguGamaliyeli indodana kaPedazuri.
\v 24 Laphezu kwebutho lesizwe sabantwana bakoBhenjamini kwakunguAbidani indodana kaGideyoni.
\p
\v 25 Kwasekusuka uphawu lwenkamba yabantwana bakoDani; babengabokucina ezinkambeni zonke\x + Josh. 6.9.\x* ngamabutho abo\x + 2.25-31.\x*; laphezu kwebutho lakhe kwakunguAhiyezeri indodana kaAmishadayi\x + 1.12,13,15.\x*.
\v 26 Laphezu kwebutho lesizwe sabantwana bakoAsheri kwakunguPagiyeli indodana kaOkirani.
\v 27 Laphezu kwebutho lesizwe sabantwana bakoNafithali kwakunguAhira indodana kaEnani.
\v 28 Lokhu yikusuka kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli ngamabutho abo, ekusukeni kwabo.
\p
\v 29 UMozisi wasesithi kuHobabi indodana kaRehuweli umMidiyani, uyisezala kaMozisi\x + Eks. 2.18.\x*: Thina siyasuka siya endaweni iN\nd kosi\nd* eyathi ngayo: Ngizalipha yona. Hamba lathi; sizakwenzela okuhle\x + Gen. 12.7.\x*, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ikhulume okuhle ngoIsrayeli\x + Gen. 32.12. Eks. 3.8; 6.7,8.\x*.
\v 30 Wasesithi kuye: Kangiyikuhamba, kodwa-ke ngizakuya elizweni lakithi lezihlotsheni zami.
\v 31 Wasesithi: Ake ungasitshiyi, ngoba uyazi lapho esingamisa khona inkamba enkangala, uzakuba ngamehlo ethu\x + Jobe 29.15.\x*.
\v 32 Kuzakuthi-ke, uba uhamba lathi, yebo, kuzakwenzeka lokho okuhle okungakho iN\nd kosi\nd* ezasenzela okuhle, sizakwenzela okuhle\x + 10.29. Hlu. 1.16; 4.11.\x*.
\p
\v 33 Basuka-ke entabeni yeN\nd kosi\nd*, uhambo lwensuku ezintathu\x + Eks. 3.1.\x*; lomtshokotsho wesivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd* wahamba phambi kwabo uhambo lwensuku ezintathu\x + Dute. 1.33. Hez. 20.6; Josh. 3.3,4,6.\x*, ukuze ubadingele indawo yokuphumula\x + Hlab. 132.8; Jer. 31.2.\x*.
\v 34 Leyezi leN\nd kosi\nd* laliphezu kwabo emini, ekusukeni kwabo enkambeni\x + Eks. 13.21.\x*.
\v 35 Kwasekusithi ekusukeni komtshokotsho, uMozisi wathi: Vuka, N\nd kosi\nd*, kazichitheke-ke izitha zakho, lalabo abakuzondayo kababaleke phambi kwakho\x + Hlab. 68.1,2.\x*.
\v 36 Ekumisweni kwawo wathi: Buyela, N\nd kosi\nd*, kuzinkulungwane ezilitshumi zezinkulungwane zakoIsrayeli.
